{"barInfo":{"barName":"骁","description":"开放自由的类贴吧式留言板","isMainBar":true,"isPublic":true},"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>现在我已经越来越依赖使用Git+Typora+Markdown来创作了，因此在命令行启动typora的方法是</p><p>在.zshrc上配置：</p><pre spellcheck=\"false\">alias typora=\"open -a typora\"\n</pre><p>然后重启终端或运行`source ~/.zshrc`，然后</p><pre spellcheck=\"false\">typora .\n</pre><p>就可以在typora上打开当前文件夹了。也可以打开某个特定文件。</p> ","floor":1,"pid":0,"postTime":"2020-04-11 11:21:52","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","sourceUrl":"","tid":3054}],"pageInfo":{"total":1,"pageSize":30,"current":1},"threadInfo":{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","classifyName":"闲谈","goodClassifyName":"","id":3054,"isGood":false,"isPicture":false,"isRepost":false,"postTime":"2020-04-11 11:21:52","replyCount":0,"title":"如何从命令行启动Typora","topState":0},"tid":3054,"total":1,"totalPages":1,"viewHost":false,"users":{"admin":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}},"needVerify":true}